                 <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">K√©o v√† th·∫£ c√°c th·∫ª t·ª´ v√†o ƒë√∫ng v·ªã tr√≠ ƒë·ªÉ t·∫°o th√†nh c·ª•m t·ª´ ho√†n ch·ªânh.</p>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-center text-gray-700">Ng√¢n h√†ng t·ª´</h3>
